title: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of Sync
description: The current issue is related to the JarExporter, which seems to be causing the application to go out of sync.
OB: When using the JarExporter, the application becomes out of sync.
EB: The exported jar file should not include itself, which will prevent the application from going out of sync.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Use the JarExporter module to export a jar file.
2. Run the exported jar file.
3. Notice that the application goes out of sync.
